headline: PURE Property Management and HomeRiver Group Merge, Secure $80 Million in Growth Capital
summary: PURE Property Management and HomeRiver Group today announced their merger, operating as PURE HomeRiver. Combined, PURE HomeRiver manages over 40,000 properties across 80+ local offices in 200+ markets and adjacent cities across 35+ states, with the vision of making renting and investing simple, smart, and more satisfying.

headline: Mizuho Raises Prudential (PRU) Target to $126, Keeps Neutral Rating
summary: Prudential Financial, Inc. (NYSE:PRU) is included among the 15 Best High Yield Stocks to Buy. On January 14, Mizuho slightly increased its price target on Prudential Financial, Inc.
